    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish paired with an interior that remains in an untouched state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, mirroring its original factory specifications. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
