    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s M-Division engineering, centered around the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This naturally aspirated straight-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully serviced with Beisan systems seals and a rattled-tuned procedure. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with structural plates, and the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells for peace of mind. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential that maintains perfect lockup. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, remains in factory-spec alignment, preserving the telepathic steering rack feedback. With flawless paint depth and a cabin devoid of typical bolster wear, this vehicle is mechanically and aesthetically sorted for the discerning collector.",
